023","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Uqbah ibn \u2018Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOne who recites the Quran publicly is like one who gives charity publicly, and one who recites privately is like one who gives charity privately.\u201d Al-Tirmidhi said, \u201cAccording to the scholars, the meaning is that\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31794,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/greed-caprice-vanity-muhlikat\/","url_meta":{"origin":34617,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Vices: Greed, caprice, and vanity are destructive vices","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThree deeds are destructive vices: greed that is obeyed, whims that are followed, and everyone impressed by their own opinion.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 3976 Grade: Hasan li ghayrihi (fair due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32373,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/19\/terrifying-punishment-kibr\/","url_meta":{"origin":34617,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Bulas: Terrifying punishment of arrogant in Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe arrogant will be gathered on the Day of Resurrection as tiny particles in the form of men. Disgrace will be cast over them from every side. They will be dragged to a prison in Hell named\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41367,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/10\/05\/sinking-until-yawm-al-qiyamah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34617,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Vanity: Proud man sinking into earth until Judgment Day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA man among those before you went out haughtily in his fine garment, so Allah ordered the earth to seize him. He is sinking into it until the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2491\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43164,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/16\/proudful-trailing\/","url_meta":{"origin":34617,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Pride: Punishment for proudful trailing clothes","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 16, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDraping is in regards to the robe, shirt, and turban. Whoever trails any of them in pride, Allah will not look at him on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4094 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32367,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/19\/kibr-habbatin-min-khardalin\/","url_meta":{"origin":34617,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Kibr: Allah throws down the arrogant in Hell","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever has the weight of a mustard seed of arrogance in his heart, Allah will throw him down on his face in Hellfire.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 7015 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0628\u062f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/34617","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=34617"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/34617\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminae